thor_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "When an expression tree is created with the AstBuilder methods (like expr_binary for example), transforming it into source format incorrectly flatten it.\n\nThis affect the output of `--pretty expanded`. It also affect the result of the to_tokens method and the result of the quote_*! macro.\n\nI made a repository with code to demonstrate issue when using quote_expr!:\nhttps://github.com/dzamlo/test_to_source_expr_flattening\n\nIts possible to manually add parentheses when building the expression as a workaround:\n\n``` rust\nlet expr = cx.expr(DUMMY_SP, ast::ExprParen(expr));\n```\n\nThe version of rust I tested with is the following:\n\n```\nrustc 0.13.0-nightly (40fb87d40 2014-11-10 23:01:57 +0000)\nbinary: rustc\ncommit-hash: 40fb87d40f681f5356af42175fc7b85da387f037\ncommit-date: 2014-11-10 23:01:57 +0000\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\nrelease: 0.13.0-nightly\n```\n", "closed_by": {"login": "dzamlo", "id": 2960379, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5NjAzNzk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2960379?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo", "html_url": "https://github.com/dzamlo", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dzamlo/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/18886/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1